# ═══════════════════════════════════════
# SATELINK — HARDENED .GITIGNORE v1.1
# ═══════════════════════════════════════

# ═══ ZONE 3 — INTERNAL PRIVATE (never move to public repo) ═══
# These files are operational security. Publishing them enables platform abuse.
# apps/api/src/monitoring/ - kept internal (SLA thresholds, sentinel)
# apps/api/src/core/operations_engine.js - kept internal (pricing logic)
# apps/api/src/workloads/auto_ops_engine.js - kept internal (auto ops engine)
# apps/api/src/ops-agent/ - kept internal (multi-agent orchestration)
# scripts/security/ - kept internal (security gate definitions)
# Do NOT add these to public repos under any circumstances.
# See docs/GOVERNANCE_ZONES.md for full classification.

